{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind","slug":"the-kite-and-the-wind","title":"The Kite and the Wind","title_ko":"연과 바람","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/cover.webp","summary_ko":"더 높이 자유롭게 날고 싶던 연 키라가 줄을 끊고서야, 진정한 자유에는 이어 주는 끈이 필요하다는 걸 배우는 이야기예요.","wordCount":120,"pages":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Kira was a bright paper kite.","translation_ko":"키라는 밝은 색의 종이 연이었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Kira","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"was","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":520,"endMs":780},{"word":"a","charStart":9,"charEnd":10,"startMs":780,"endMs":1120},{"word":"bright","charStart":11,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1220},{"word":"paper","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1660},{"word":"kite","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1660,"endMs":1920}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"She longed to fly higher than anyone.","translation_ko":"키라는 누구보다 높이 날기를 간절히 바랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"longed","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":460,"endMs":980},{"word":"to","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":980,"endMs":1180},{"word":"fly","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1380},{"word":"higher","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1860},{"word":"than","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2200},{"word":"anyone","charStart":30,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2480}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"Every day, the Wind came to play.","translation_ko":"매일, 바람이 놀러 왔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Every","charStart":0,"charEnd":5,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"day","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":400,"endMs":720},{"word":"the","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":880,"endMs":1040},{"word":"Wind","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1040,"endMs":1260},{"word":"came","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1600},{"word":"to","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1820},{"word":"play","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2040}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"Together they soared above the green hills.","translation_ko":"둘은 함께 푸른 언덕 위로 날아올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Together","charStart":0,"charEnd":8,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"they","charStart":9,"charEnd":13,"startMs":400,"endMs":780},{"word":"soared","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":780,"endMs":1100},{"word":"above","charStart":21,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1340},{"word":"the","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1640},{"word":"green","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1900},{"word":"hills","charStart":37,"charEnd":42,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2300}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"But Kira always felt the string that held her.","translation_ko":"하지만 키라는 늘 자기를 붙잡은 줄을 느꼈어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"Kira","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":420,"endMs":800},{"word":"always","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":800,"endMs":1520},{"word":"felt","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1840},{"word":"the","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2300},{"word":"string","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2520},{"word":"that","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2980},{"word":"held","charStart":37,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2980,"endMs":2980},{"word":"her","charStart":42,"charEnd":45,"startMs":2980,"endMs":3180}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"If only I were free,\" she sighed.","translation_ko":"\"내가 자유롭기만 하다면.\" 키라는 한숨지었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"If","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":620},{"word":"only","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":620,"endMs":1020},{"word":"I","charStart":9,"charEnd":10,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1260},{"word":"were","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1500},{"word":"free","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1820},{"word":"she","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2320},{"word":"sighed","charStart":27,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2680}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"Cut me loose!\" she begged the Wind.","translation_ko":"\"나를 풀어 줘!\" 키라가 바람에게 애원했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Cut","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"me","charStart":5,"charEnd":7,"startMs":280,"endMs":540},{"word":"loose","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":540,"endMs":840},{"word":"she","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1640},{"word":"begged","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1820},{"word":"the","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2060},{"word":"Wind","charStart":31,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2260}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"So the Wind tugged until the string broke.","translation_ko":"그래서 바람이 잡아당겨 마침내 줄이 끊어졌어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":560},{"word":"the","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":560,"endMs":1000},{"word":"Wind","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1400},{"word":"tugged","charStart":12,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1400,"endMs":2180},{"word":"until","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":2180,"endMs":2720},{"word":"the","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2720,"endMs":3080},{"word":"string","charStart":29,"charEnd":35,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3320},{"word":"broke","charStart":36,"charEnd":41,"startMs":3320,"endMs":3740}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"At first, Kira danced with joy.","translation_ko":"처음에 키라는 기뻐서 춤을 췄어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"At","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"first","charStart":3,"charEnd":8,"startMs":220,"endMs":660},{"word":"Kira","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1340},{"word":"danced","charStart":15,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1740},{"word":"with","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2060},{"word":"joy","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2280}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"She tumbled and spun through the open sky.","translation_ko":"키라는 탁 트인 하늘을 데굴데굴 돌며 날았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"tumbled","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":340,"endMs":800},{"word":"and","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":800,"endMs":1500},{"word":"spun","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1720},{"word":"through","charStart":21,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2040},{"word":"the","charStart":29,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2340},{"word":"open","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2500},{"word":"sky","charStart":38,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2500,"endMs":2900}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"But without the string, she could not steer.","translation_ko":"하지만 줄이 없으니 방향을 잡을 수 없었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"without","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":320,"endMs":700},{"word":"the","charStart":12,"charEnd":15,"startMs":700,"endMs":1000},{"word":"string","charStart":16,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1260},{"word":"she","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1800},{"word":"could","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1800,"endMs":1960},{"word":"not","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1960,"endMs":2380},{"word":"steer","charStart":38,"charEnd":43,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2640}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"The Wind pushed her far from home.","translation_ko":"바람은 키라를 집에서 멀리 밀어냈어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"Wind","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":680},{"word":"pushed","charStart":9,"charEnd":15,"startMs":680,"endMs":1120},{"word":"her","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1120,"endMs":1380},{"word":"far","charStart":20,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1740},{"word":"from","charStart":24,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2040},{"word":"home","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2380}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then a gentle hand caught her in a meadow.","translation_ko":"그때 들판에서 부드러운 손이 키라를 받아 줬어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":380},{"word":"a","charStart":5,"charEnd":6,"startMs":380,"endMs":760},{"word":"gentle","charStart":7,"charEnd":13,"startMs":760,"endMs":1100},{"word":"hand","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1500},{"word":"caught","charStart":19,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1800},{"word":"her","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1800,"endMs":2040},{"word":"in","charStart":30,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2200},{"word":"a","charStart":33,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2200,"endMs":2460},{"word":"meadow","charStart":35,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2500}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"It was the child who had flown her.","translation_ko":"키라를 날리던 바로 그 아이였어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":15,"endMs":245},{"word":"was","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":245,"endMs":475},{"word":"the","charStart":7,"charEnd":10,"startMs":475,"endMs":706},{"word":"child","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":706,"endMs":936},{"word":"who","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":936,"endMs":1166},{"word":"had","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1166,"endMs":1396},{"word":"flown","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1396,"endMs":1626},{"word":"her","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1626,"endMs":2010}]}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"The child tied a new string with care.","translation_ko":"아이는 정성껏 새 줄을 매어 줬어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"child","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":220,"endMs":600},{"word":"tied","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":600,"endMs":980},{"word":"a","charStart":15,"charEnd":16,"startMs":980,"endMs":1200},{"word":"new","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1400},{"word":"string","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1700},{"word":"with","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1980},{"word":"care","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":1980,"endMs":2260}]},{"id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"Now Kira flies free, and is never alone.","translation_ko":"이제 키라는 자유롭게, 그리고 결코 혼자가 아닌 채로 날아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-kite-and-the-wind/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":580},{"word":"Kira","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":680,"endMs":940},{"word":"flies","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":940,"endMs":1400},{"word":"free","charStart":15,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1780},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2220},{"word":"is","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2220,"endMs":2460},{"word":"never","charStart":28,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2700},{"word":"alone","charStart":34,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3120}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"연 키라는 무엇을 간절히 바랐나요?","type":"mc","options":["바람을 멈추는 것","누구보다 높이 자유롭게 나는 것","색이 바뀌는 것","땅에 내려오는 것"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"키라는 자기를 붙잡은 줄을 느끼며, 누구보다 높이 자유롭게 날기를 바랐어요.","id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"키라는 바람에게 무엇을 부탁했나요?","type":"mc","options":["집으로 데려가 달라고","더 천천히 불어 달라고","비를 내려 달라고","줄을 끊어 자유롭게 해 달라고"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"\"나를 풀어 줘!\"라며 줄을 끊어 달라고 애원했어요.","id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"줄이 끊어진 뒤 키라에게 생긴 문제는 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["바람이 사라졌다","더 높이 잘 날게 되었다","색이 사라졌다","방향을 잡을 수 없어 멀리 밀려갔다"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"줄이 없으니 방향을 잡을 수 없었고, 바람이 키라를 집에서 멀리 밀어냈어요.","id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"들판에서 키라를 받아 준 것은 누구인가요?","type":"mc","options":["새","키라를 날리던 아이","농부","다른 연"],"answerIndex":1,"explain_ko":"부드러운 손이 키라를 받아 줬는데, 바로 키라를 날리던 그 아이였어요.","id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 전하는 메시지는 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["진정한 자유에는 이어 주는 끈이 필요하다","바람은 믿으면 안 된다","줄은 무조건 나쁘다","혼자가 가장 자유롭다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"아이가 새 줄을 매어 주자 키라는 자유롭게, 그러나 혼자가 아닌 채로 날 수 있었어요 — 진짜 자유에는 연결이 필요하다는 뜻이에요.","id":"the-kite-and-the-wind-q5","ord":4}]}